{"tid":1517340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳浩天被捕　警方稱涉參與暴動及襲警","createTime":"2019-08-30T01:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:11:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"47b6d04078a8026b9bad69fbbaf0f2d5169fedec","tid":1517340,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"已被取締的香港民族黨，召集人陳浩天昨晚在社交網站表示，於香港機場預備出境時被扣留。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，有組織罪案及三合會調查科昨晚於機場拘捕一名29歲姓陳的男子，涉嫌「參與暴動」及「襲警」，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方本月初在火炭一間工廈拘捕7男1女，涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器及無牌管有爆炸品，被捕人士包括陳浩天，他當時被扣留約43小時後獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477703-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477703-20190830.htm&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=c4786bc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477703-20190830.htm&h=90db181b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477703-20190830.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5fb28deb887f0790fcef4bf2d92ba6295fe90192","tid":1517340,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:58:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e55c8c45fe20c249f615512c9e603a3d0f3f5002","tid":1517340,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCbR8vr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCbR8vr.jpg&h=852141d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZDtrg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZDtrg8.jpg&h=8c62ce99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isWiOvB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FisWiOvB.jpg&h=94c1ec27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ae8110bf00c3a2a11e309c92278742f39cf36a4","tid":1517340,"uid":189109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score"